-- ft.page.body:

-- pd.package: Fastn Powered by Footer
name: fastn-community.github.io/footer

`fastn-footer` is another footer component which shows powered by text with
fastn logo and link to fifthtry.com.

Use our `fastn-footer` on your fastn web projects, and give us credit.

If you are using our `doc-site` as your website theme, then to use
`fastn-footer` add below `fastn` dependency into `FASTN.ftd` file:

-- ft.code:
lang: ftd

\-- fastn.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/doc-site
\-- fastn.dependency: fastn-community.github.io/footer
\-- fastn.auto-import: fifthtry.github.io/doc-site as ds
\-- fastn.auto-import: fastn-community.github.io/footer

-- tf.markdown:

Once you add above lines into your `fastn` package, add `footer` into your
`.ftd` file like shown in below code snippet. 

Below example code is to add footer if you are using `doc-site` as your website
thme.

-- cb.rendered:

-- cb.rendered.input:

\-- ds.page: Title of the page
show-footer: true

\-- ds.page.footer: 

\-- footer.fastn-footer:
copyright: Copyright © 2023 - [FifthTry](https://www.fifthtry.com/)
site-logo: https://fastn.com/-/fastn.com/images/fastn.svg
powered-by-text: Powered by
powered-by-link: https://fastn.com/

\-- ds.page.body:
Some page body components and content here

\-- end: ds.page

-- cb.rendered.output:

-- tf.markdown:

Look at the bottom of this page.

-- end: cb.rendered.output

-- end: cb.rendered

-- end: ft.page
